SCP Neurosplit
Isometric Creature Collector

Kultist Stats:
-	Hp
-	Xp
-	Attack
-	Def
-	Speed
-	Reaction

Kultist Types:
-	Flame
-	Plant
-	Water
-	Ice
-	Toxic
-	Anomalous
-	Paranormal
-	Biomechanical

Reactions:
-	Vaporize
-	Freeze
-	Sludge

Player Xp:
-	Get a lootbox for every level up
-	Dying doesn’t remove any items, but gives xp debt

Kultist Xp:
-	Small Enchantment Seed – gives 1 xp level
-	Enchantment Seed – gives 2 xp levels
-	Mega Enchantment Seed – gives 5 xp levels

Map:
-	Node based system
-	When a node reaches level 10 it locks all adjacent nodes at 10 levels behind it
-	Xp gained in a node by any player will contribute to that nodes xp
-	Node Types
o	City Nodes

Dupli-Race:
-	Group running math minigame
o	Vertical runner on a straight path with various obstacles that give +/-n amount of points
o	Players must build up enough points to clear each stage
-	Agility xp

Time hop:
-	

Memory Palace
-	Word search game



